No. 10A422. Minnesota Citizens Concerned for Life, Inc., et al., Applicants v. Lori Swanson, Attorney General of Minnesota, et al. 562 U.S. 997, 131 S. Ct. 446,

178 L. Ed. 2d 347,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 8329. October 29, 2010.

Application for an injunction pending appeal, presented to Justice Alito, and by him referred to the Court, denied.
